title: Seed-Crusted Venison Steak & Roast Veggie Toss with Yoghurt
description: It’s a good idea to have an extra layer on you, but how about on tonight’s dinner? Let’s add layers upon layers of flavour
by crusting the venison steak in pumpkin seeds, our Aussie spice blend and golden breadcrumbs for a crunchy texture. Cook it
up and serve with a tangy yoghurt.
